summary: Contains pretty much all of the record titles and their corresponding Form IDs. Very useful for TESsnip modding.
descriptionHtml:
Contains pretty much all of the record titles and their corresponding Form IDs. Very useful for TESsnip. Only ones I know are missing at the moment are:

- Ingestible
- Animated Object
- Cell
- Climate
- Idle Animation
- Image Space Modifier
- Quest
- Race
- Voice Type
- Worldspace

Will update once they\'re done.
author: Xylozi
